				<font color="#f0f8ff" face="Arial,Helvetica,Geneva,Swiss,SunSans-Regular"><b>D i g i &nbsp; B o o s t e r &nbsp; P r o f e s s i o n a l &nbsp; v 2 . 2 1</b></font>
			</td></tr>
			<tr><td width="100%" height="15" bgcolor="#d8ecfd" align="center">
				<font color="#000066" size="2" face="Arial,Helvetica,Geneva,Swiss,SunSans-Regular">Teemu Pohjanlehto &lt;<a href="mailto:rebb@amigascne.org">rebb@amigascne.org</a>&gt;</font>
			</td></tr>
